dBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"雲龍兄無父無母<br />\n聽聞上次得兩個朋友去聲援<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0bb50c5800a0c366c6658ca57074559d5aa0fa0","tid":1598822,"uid":57073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"【他在欄內  向旁聽席望了兩次】<br />\n<br />\n只是19歲的他，賴雲龍，在7月14日沙田遊行中因為涉嫌襲警被捕。身有官司的他無所畏懼，8月12日參與了機場「警察還眼行動」。期間，「真國安假記者」付國豪被示威者發現、圍毆。事後，賴雲龍再次被捕，被控非法集結、襲擊致造成身體傷害。8月19日提堂，法官不準他保釋，須要還柙。<br />\n<br />\n據媒體報道，賴雲龍父母離異，他自己一人獨居。<br />\n<br />\n8月27日下午2點半，賴雲龍再次提堂，進行保釋覆核。<br />\n<br />\n下午的旁聽席，案件不多，人不多，被告及聽審的親屬不過寥寥數人，十分冷清。<br />\n<br />\n有二位女士來聲援，一位是黃女士、一位是Vivian。<br />\n<br />\n開庭了，穿著黑長薄衣、黑長褲的賴雲龍從內庭疾步走到犯人欄，他快速看了一眼觀眾席，便轉過身去，面向法官，雙手合放背後。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師以沙田襲警案另一被獲准保釋為理由，以及15000元現金擔保、每天晚上6至9時到就近警署報到及遵守晚上8時至翌日8時的宵禁令為新保釋條件，但裁判官以案件無重大改變而拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n知道覆核失敗，賴雲龍唯有轉身再走回內庭囚室，他又向旁聽席望了一次。黃女士大力向他揮手。黃女士說，向他揮手，是希望他知道有人來支持他，他並不孤單。<br />\n<br />\n散庭後，黃女士和Vivian，還有數位記者，一直在法庭停車場等候賴雲龍的囚車離開法庭。大約五點，囚車駛離法庭。黃女士、Vivian大聲高叫：「手足，支持你！」黃女士又大力拍打車身，希望縱使在車內的賴雲龍聽不到大家的叫聲，也收到大家的心意。<br />\n<br />\n賴雲龍沙田襲警一案，於10月4日上午於沙田裁判法院進行答辯；機場警察還眼一案，則於10月28日東區法院再次提堂。<br />\n<br />\n圖片：明報  文字：李遨<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n支持Resistance Live Media，為大家帶來前線抗爭消息，請Like/Follow：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/resistancelive2014/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fresistancelive2014%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=fceb6e42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/resistancelive2014/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2368697036727971&amp;id=1432983410299343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2368697036727971%26id%3D1432983410299343&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=121bfd07\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2368697036727971&amp;id=1432983410299343</a>"},{"pid":"9f690e9694cf7133e7fc19908bd87b9f39ff962c","tid":1598822,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30f0052f307cafb8596a098b3f04ba111dc5f5e","tid":1598822,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd74f9ccd2394622dcfc5990ddb7749ec8417414","tid":1598822,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2568ee4b93ddf72a8f93d17e8b5c7098e18c605","tid":1598822,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40d0c1865968bc7e91b789a25a03b653f5699996","tid":1598822,"uid":57073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2cf4a8fa2f96e9f708524afc5d1c19b1a920bb5","tid":1598822,"uid":81947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:18:33.000Z","msg":"請假過嚟，到時見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"我應該都請假去"},{"pid":"30331164fbcf3e1b07fe470c3674d38a92dabb3d","tid":1598822,"uid":181659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:29:43.000Z","msg":"推 支持支持"},{"pid":"490460878c9a4a5f16e7f1ae147cf7c661b29704","tid":1598822,"uid":104811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:33:23.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4c19b740b835915a4d5b3af8dbfd45a31190d43e","tid":1598822,"uid":166222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"推 準時到<br />\n兄弟 You&rsquo;ll never walk alone."},{"pid":"fec38b06468e3ae7ddb0a33d1360e5ae140c3565","tid":1598822,"uid":48642,"like"