叫聲，也收到大家的心意。<br />\n<br />\n賴雲龍沙田襲警一案，於10月4日上午於沙田裁判法院進行答辯；機場警察還眼一案，則於10月28日東區法院再次提堂。<br />\n<br />\n圖片：明報  文字：李遨<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n支持Resistance Live Media，為大家帶來前線抗爭消息，請Like/Follow：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/resistancelive2014/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fresistancelive2014%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=fceb6e42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/resistancelive2014/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2368697036727971&amp;id=1432983410299343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2368697036727971%26id%3D1432983410299343&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=121bfd07\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2368697036727971&amp;id=1432983410299343</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"成篇文讀得出有哀傷味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:39:19.000Z","msg":"vivian 好似係c9 來<br />\n唉<br />\n<br />\n你諗下雲龍義士係咩feel<br />\n一個後生都無 被人當condom <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc39484fd4dc39651d3f87a5ac0c0bb7153d852","tid":1598822,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee3b62d2aa7f88821d0569d03a3487ad986932a","tid":1598822,"uid":281980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e641daccf5b1117c29158c28b7899fdcd950b31","tid":1598822,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220e02c067865c04f21f6ba8979b2bdb5f4deecd","tid":1598822,"uid":281181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"